	(363, 'km', 'Thai', 'ความเป็นมาของโครงการ', 'Background of the Project', '', 'In 2014, the National Council for Peace and Order (NCPO) passed a resolution in a meeting held on 2 July 2014, approving in principle the Ministry of Defense (Army) to proceed with the project of building a precious wood museum by asking the Office of the Permanent Secretary of the Prime Minister&rsquo;s Office to set the annual expenditure budget for the Ministry of Defense (Army) as a disbursement unit for construction in the area of the Royal Thai Army Auditorium, Dusit District, Bangkok, with the size of 8 Rai. Later, His Majesty the King granted land in Wang Thonglang, Bangkok, another 36 Rai to be used in the museum&rsquo;s construction. Therefore, the Fine Arts Department had to adjust the designs and estimate new costs to suit the area size. After that, the Fine Arts Department completed the new design and evaluated the new costs, and the Office of the Permanent Secretary of the Prime Minister&rsquo;s Office proposed to the Cabinet on 4 January 2022 to review and consider the agency responsible for proposing budgets for project implementation according to the Cabinet resolution on 30 April 2019, by suggesting the Ministry of Natural Resources and Environment (MNRE) to responsible for proposing a budget for the museum&rsquo;s construction project from the fiscal year 2023 onwards, including the annual management and maintenance budget. On 11 January 2022, the Cabinet approved the budget for the museum construction project for 4,055,318,000 baht to be used for construction during the fiscal year 2023-2027, respectively.', 37, 'MNRE HUB', '2023-01-18 16:45:26', '2023-04-19 13:39:45', 'Enable', 79, 38, 'ผู้ดูแลระบบ สพท.', '', 278, 337),
	(364, 'km', 'Thai', 'วัตถุประสงค์', 'Objectives', '', '1. To honor His Majesty Phrabat Somdet Phra Boromchanakadhipeshra Maha Bhumibol Adulyadej Maharaj Borommanat Pobitra on the auspicious occasion of His Majesty the King&rsquo;s 70th accession to the throne on 9 June 2016, in honor of Her Majesty Queen Sirikit The Queen Mother&rsquo;s birthday on the auspicious occasion of her 7th cycle (every 12 years) birthday anniversary on 12 August 2016, and on the auspicious occasion of her coronation.\r\n\r\n2. To make use of valuable wood under the supervision of the government to build a museum displaying knowledge about precious wood of Thailand, which will cause love and cherish the precious forest resources, create a collective consciousness in the protection, caring, and restoration of the national forest resources, as well as being a learning center for Thai people and foreign tourists who come to visit. It can also serve as a place to welcome royal family members or government guests.', 37, 'MNRE HUB', '2023-01-18 16:45:35', '2023-04-19 13:40:16', 'Enable', 80, 38, 'ผู้ดูแลระบบ สพท.', '', 278, 337),
	(365, 'km', 'Thai', 'ที่ตั้ง', 'Location', '', 'The building site of the Precious Wood Knowledge Museum for the benefit of the Kingdom on the auspicious occasion of the coronation is located on the land bestowed by His Majesty the King at Pradit Manutham Road, Wang Thonglang District, Bangkok, with an area of 79 Rai 2 Ngan 60.9 square Wa (36 Rai for the construction of the museum and the construction of a multipurpose hall building 40 Rai.)', 37, 'MNRE HUB', '2023-01-18 16:45:45', '2023-04-19 13:41:20', 'Enable', 81, 38, 'ผู้ดูแลระบบ สพท.', '', 278, 337),
	(366, 'km', 'Thai', 'ลักษณะของโครงการ', 'Project Details and the Location', '', 'Project Details: The museum building is designed to emphasize applied Thai architecture. It established the building in the form of 3 pearls, gabled, with a total height of 4 floors, a usable area of approximately 25,000 square meters, consisting of;\r\n  - The B1 and B2 floors as a parking lot\r\n  - The 1st floor consists of a stair hall, a reception/public relations room, a lecture room on the history of Thailand, an exhibition room, a souvenir shop, and an office.\r\n  - The 2nd floor consists of meeting rooms/reception rooms', 37, 'MNRE HUB', '2023-01-18 16:45:52', '2023-04-19 13:41:04', 'Enable', 82, 38, 'ผู้ดูแลระบบ สพท.', '', 278, 337),
